440
01:23:35.802 --> 01:23:37.012
Don't make a sound.

441
01:23:39.180 --> 01:23:40.015
My father...

442
01:23:40.765 --> 01:23:42.267
I'll check on him.

443
01:23:42.308 --> 01:23:45.020
For now. just stay quiet
and don't go anywhere. okay?

444
01:23:54.904 --> 01:23:56.239
