446
01:24:06.416 --> 01:24:07.250
Hold on. Hold on.

447
01:24:11.212 --> 01:24:12.380
Keep pushing.

448
01:24:28.396 --> 01:24:29.397
Stop!

449
01:24:32.525 --> 01:24:33.443
